race.comment: Looks a race in three between RECIPROCAL (3), FLAMING NAVY (1) and UTAH (2). RECIPROCAL is first-up after being tried in some strong 3YO races during the autumn. Suspect he will be better over further but he might have a class edge over his rivals in this grade. He will likely concede a start but can be finishing hard. FLAMING NAVY was solid after leading first-up and, with the benefit of that run, can be hard to catch here if connections adopt the same tactics. He's drawn well and the claim helps. UTAH is a last start maiden winner that can go on with the job in this grade. Outside of that trio, MAGIC PRINCESS (5) and HAYAI MESU (8) are worth some thought.
